(71, 'Zarrab&#39;ın Mahkeme tarihi belli oldu', '/upload/m66813m853957051.jpg', 13, '<h2 class=&quot;ustblkgenislet2 spot &quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 17px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #666666; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif !important;&quot;>New York&#39;ta tutuklu bulunan Reza Zarrab&#39;ın d&uuml;n yaptığı kefalet başvurusuna mahkemeden cevap geldi.</h2>\r\n<p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; float: none; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; color: #333333; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal !important;&quot;><a class=&quot;keyword&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: none; color: #333333 !important; cursor: pointer !important; font-stretch: normal !important;&quot; title=&quot;New York Haberleri&quot; href=&quot;http://www.haberler.com/new-york/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;>New York</a>&nbsp;G&uuml;ney B&ouml;lge Hakimi Richard M. Berman,&nbsp;<a class=&quot;keyword&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration: none; color: #333333 !important; cursor: pointer !important; font-stretch: normal !important;&quot; title=&quot;Başsavcılık Haberleri&quot; href=&quot;http://www.haberler.com/bassavcilik/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;>Başsavcılık</a>&nbsp;makamından Zarrab&#39;ın talebine 25 Mayıs 2016 tarihine kadar resmi cevap vermesini istedi.</p>\r\n<p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; float: none; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; color: #333333; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal !important;&quot;><strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;>MAHKEME TARİHİ 2 HAZİRAN 2016&#39;DA</strong></p>\r\n<p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; float: none; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; color: #333333; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal !important;&quot;>Berman, Zarrab&