(93, 'Steam&#39;in Büyük Yaz İndirimleri Ne Zaman Başlıyor?', '/upload/i54940i502097743.jpg', 20, '<p><span style=&quot;color: #22262a; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 30.6px;&quot;>Valve&#39;in merakla beklenen Steam Yaz İndirimleri hakkında g&uuml;n detayı ortaya &ccedil;ıktı.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 24.65px;&quot;>Son d&ouml;nemlerde online alışverişin artması ile beraber &ouml;zellikle &uuml;lkemizde korsan oyunculuk oranı ciddi oranda azaldı.&nbsp;</span><strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24.65px; color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;&quot;><a class=&quot;box-link&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333 !important; text-decoration: none; line-height: inherit; cursor: pointer; padding: 1px 4px !important; background: #e6e6e6;&quot; href=&quot;http://www.webtekno.com/steam&quot;>Steam</a></strong><span style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 24.65px;&quot;>,&nbsp;</span><strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24.65px; color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;&quot;>Origin&nbsp;</strong><span style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 24.65px;&quot;>ve&nbsp;</span><strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24.65px; color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;&quot;>PlayStore&nbsp;</strong><span style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 24.65px;&quot;>gibi platformların ortaya &ccedil;ıkması ile internet &uuml;zerinden yapılan&nbsp;</span><a class=&quot;box-link&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: non