(103, 'Bill Gates&#39;in Tweetine Yapılacak Her Retweet&#39;te 10 Dolar Bağış!', '/upload/m42738m333417305.jpg', 14, '<p><span style=&quot;color: #22262a; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 30.6px;&quot;>Sosyal medyada fazlasıyla rastladığımız bağış &uuml;zerine dolandırıcılığa karşı a&ccedil;ılan #RedNoseDay etiketi ile Bill Gates, her retweet&#39;e 10 Dolar bağış verecek.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 24.65px;&quot;>&Ouml;zellikle&nbsp;</span><strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24.65px; color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;&quot;><a class=&quot;box-link&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333 !important; text-decoration: none; line-height: inherit; cursor: pointer; padding: 1px 4px !important; background: #e6e6e6;&quot; href=&quot;http://www.webtekno.com/facebook&quot;>Facebook</a></strong><span style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 24.65px;&quot;>&nbsp;olmak &uuml;zere bağış toplama bahanesiyle bir&ccedil;ok sa&ccedil;ma sapan paylaşımlar g&ouml;r&uuml;yoruz. &Ouml;zellikle anne babalarımız gibi sosyal medyayı pek bilmeyen kişiler tarafından ilgi g&ouml;ren bu durumlarda k&ouml;t&uuml; halde g&ouml;z&uuml;ken hastalıklı bir &ccedil;ocuğun resmi servis edilerek &quot;</span><strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24.65px; color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;&quot;>Facebook her beğeni i&ccedil;in 5, her paylaşım i&ccedil;in 10 Dolar para veriyor</strong><span style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 24.65px;&quot;>&quot; gibi kandırmalar ile sayfanın hiti y&uuml;kseltilmekte.</span><br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 24.65px;&quot; /><br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 24.65px;&quot; /><span style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 24.65px;&quot;>İnsanların vicdanı ile oynayarak alınan destek sonrasında</span><strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24.65px; color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;&quot;>Ayşe İ&ccedil;in Yardım&nbsp;</strong><span style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 24.65px;&quot;>adındaki sayfanın daha sonradan satılarak&nbsp;</span><strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24.65px; color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;&quot;>Ankara Escort</strong><span style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 24.65px;&quot;>&nbsp;olarak değiştiğini fazlan g&ouml;rm&uuml;şs&uuml;n&uuml;zd&uuml;r. İşte tam bu duruma dikkat &ccedil;ekmek i&ccedil;in&nbsp;</span><strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24.65px; color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;&quot;>#RedNoseDay</strong><span style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 24.65px;&quot;>&nbsp;etiketi ile &ccedil;aışma başlatan&nbsp;</span><a class=&quot;box-link&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; line-height: 24.65px; cursor: pointer; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; color: #333333 !important; padding: 1px 4px !important; background: #e6e6e6;&quot; href=&quot;http://www.webtekno.com/twitter&quot;>Twitter</a><span style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 24.65px;&quot;>, bir&ccedil;ok &uuml;nl&uuml; ismin de desteğini alarak &ccedil;ocuklar i&ccedil;in yardım kampanyası d&uuml;zenliyor.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 24.65px;&quot;>Bu bağlamda teknoloji sekt&ouml;r&uuml;n&uuml;n en bilinen isimlerinden olan&nbsp;</span><strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24.65px; color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;&quot;><a class=&quot;box-link&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333 !important; text-decoration: none; line-height: inherit; cursor: pointer; padding: 1px 4px !important; background: #e6e6e6;&quot; href=&quot;http://www.webtekno.com/microsoft&quot;>Microsoft</a></strong><span style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 24.65px;&quot;>&#39;un kurucusu&nbsp;</span><strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 24.65px; color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;&quot;>Bill Gates</strong><span style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 24.65px;&quot;>, bu kampanyaya kendisi de katıldı.&nbsp;</span><a style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; line-height: 24.65px; cursor: pointer; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; color: #0000ee !important;&quot; href=&quot;https://twitter.com/BillGates/status/733332967540461568?utm_source=webtekno&amp;utm_medium=bill-gates-in-tweetine-yapilacak-her-retweet-te-10-dolar-bagis&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;><strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;&quot;>Buradan</strong></a><span style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: &#39;PT Sans&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 24.65px;&quot;>&nbsp;g&ouml;rebiliceğiniz Bill Gates&#39;in tweetini</span><stron